## Decision Matrix

| Category | Pass | Modify | Block |
|----------|------|--------|-------|
| Environment | Fully containerized | Mostly pinned | Unpinned deps |
| Data versioning | Hashed and versioned | Versioned | No versioning |
| Code state | Git SHA + clean tree | SHA recorded | No version tracking |
| Random seeds | All seeded, verified | Mostly seeded | No seed management |
| Compute spec | Fully documented | Partially documented | Not documented |
| Reproduction test | Independent verification | Author-verified | Not tested |

---

## Final Verdict

- [ ] **Proceed**: Results are reproducible with documented process
- [ ] **Modify**: Address gaps before publishing / merging
- [ ] **Spike**: Run independent reproduction attempt to validate
- [ ] **Escalate**: Fundamental reproducibility concern requires redesign
